<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich Kügelein, Bürger zu Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat lädt Kügelein unverzüglich vor.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_271" id="135v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_271_r1l10"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Kügelın <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_271_r1l11"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> wır <expan>heıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd manen dıch <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> auf den aıd den du </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l12">vns geſworn haſt / daʒ du <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> nach angeſıcht dıcʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l13">ʒu vns herein komeſt / vnd auch niht von vns <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> auſʒıeheſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l14">on <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> wort / wan wır mıt dır ʒu reden <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vnd des mıt nichte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l15">laſſeſt . daran tuſt du <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l16"><expan>Remi<ex>ni</ex>ſce<ex>re</ex></expan> <expan>A<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> etc xvȷ<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_271" id="135v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Kügelin, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich,</ex></expan> wir <expan>heiss<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                        manen dich <expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan> auf den aid, den du uns gesworn
                        hast, daz du <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> nach angesicht
                        dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> zu uns herein komest und auch niht von
                        uns <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> ausziehest on
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> wort, wan wir mit dir zu reden
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und des mit nichte lassest, daran
                        tust du <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>remi<ex>ni</ex>sce<ex>re</ex></expan>
<expan>a<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> etc. xvi<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
